# Quality Checklist - MANDATORY Before Marking Work Complete

## ‚úÖ Pre-Completion Validation

### **Technical Validation**
- [ ] **Full Test Suite**: `./scripts/quality/validate-system.sh` passes 100%
- [ ] **Integration Tests**: All Spring Boot contexts load successfully  
- [ ] **Core Workflows**: Document upload, authentication, search functional
- [ ] **Error Handling**: No HTTP 500 errors in normal operations
- [ ] **Database Operations**: All CRUD operations working
- [ ] **Service Health**: All actuator endpoints healthy

### **Production Readiness**  
- [ ] **Environment Testing**: `docker-compose up -d` successful
- [ ] **Service Communication**: Inter-service calls working
- [ ] **Security**: Authentication/authorization functional
- [ ] **Performance**: Response times acceptable
- [ ] **Monitoring**: Health checks operational

### **Documentation & Deployment**
- [ ] **API Documentation**: Updated for endpoint changes
- [ ] **Configuration**: Environment variables documented
- [ ] **Deployment Guide**: Production deployment steps
- [ ] **Rollback Plan**: Steps to revert if needed

## üö´ Quality Gates

### **STOP WORK if ANY of these are true:**
- [ ] Any test failures exist
- [ ] HTTP 500 errors in core functionality  
- [ ] Spring Boot contexts fail to load
- [ ] Database operations failing
- [ ] Service startup failures
- [ ] Core user workflows broken

### **NEVER claim "Done" unless:**
- [ ] 100% test pass rate
- [ ] All functionality manually verified
- [ ] Zero known bugs or errors
- [ ] Production deployment validated
- [ ] Documentation complete

